# Version Management Standards

<version>1.0.0</version>

## Context
- On code generated, always use the proper package's versions.
- Rules on new package installation.

## Requirements

### Dependencies management

- Never install new package directly, always ask user
- Avoid installation new packages if you can use current ones
- Prefer stable versions

## Critical Rules

<critical>
- ALWAYS get approval before adding new dependencies
- ALWAYS specify exact versions for production dependencies
</critical> 
